title: Babe (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)
description:
Babe is another bop that Taylor passed on to another country artist! Is 'babe' the most intimate thing that you can call someone? Are you guilty of using the word or are you more of a 'nay' to the babe? Plus, the meaning behind this song and Taylor's intent with it! And, lots of personal trigger warnings in this episode!
What did we miss? What else would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to contact us!
